.TH LATTE-DOCK 1 "July 2026" "Lattecotta Dock 0.10.77" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
latte-dock \- dock-style launcher and task manager for Plasma 6
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B latte-dock
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B latte-dock
runs Lattecotta Dock in a Plasma Wayland session. It provides launchers,
task management, indicator themes, multiple layouts, and parabolic icon
effects.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h , " " \-\-help , " " \-\-help-all
Show command-line help.
.TP
.BR \-v , " " \-\-version
Show version information.
.TP
.BR \-r , " " \-\-replace
Replace the running Latte instance.
.TP
.BR \-d , " " \-\-debug
Write debugging messages to standard output.
.TP
.BI \-\-layout " name"
Load the named layout at startup.
.TP
.B \-\-default-layout
Import and load the default layout at startup.
.TP
.BR \-\-available-layouts , " " \-\-available-dock-templates , " " \-\-available-layout-templates
List the available layouts, dock templates, or layout templates.
.TP
.BI \-\-import-layout " absolute-file"
Import and load a layout file.
.TP
.BI \-\-suggested-layout-name " name"
Set the suggested name used with an imported layout.
.TP
.BI \-\-import-full " file"
Import a complete configuration.
.TP
.BI \-\-add-dock " template"
Add a dock or panel from the named template.
.TP
.BR \-\-single , " " \-\-multiple
Use single-layout or activity-based multiple-layout memory mode.
.TP
.BR \-\-enable-autostart , " " \-\-disable-autostart
Enable or disable application autostart.
.TP
.BR \-\-cc , " " \-\-clear-cache
Clear the QML cache before startup.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR plasmashell (1),
.BR kwin_wayland (1)
